__e: They'd laugh their asses off, and you'd probably tell them you were doing it with me so they'd forgive you for being seen with me.
You can drink yourself stupid, you can go on and call me a liar, but don't you hold me up for what happened to that little girl.
Legally you could beat me to death, and there would be no penalty.
But they're starving to death on the other side of it.
And some jackass killed her because of it.
I can build a car in six months and in six seconds, these jerks write it off as a stunt that won't even make it into the movie.
